page.title: 14Canterbury Clubs & Societies
page.content: The main{clubs}in Canterbury fall under 5 main catagories; political, {social,}sporting,{charity}and{youth.} POLITICAL-Conservative club, Liberal Party, Labour Party, National Front, Ecology Party. SOCIAL-Bridge Palace Country Club, British Legion, County Club residents, Canterbury Bowling Club, Canterbury Angling Club, Chantry Social Club, Chartham Mill Social Club, Chaucer Club, Chislet Colliery Welfare Club, Odd fellows Club, Kent and Canterbury Club, Canterbury Club, Regal EMI Bingo Club, Sturry Court Club, Sturry Rd Area Club. SPORTS CLUBS-Robert Brett & Sons Sports Club, Canterbury City Football Club, Canterbury Rugby Club, Canterbury Squash Club, Kent County Cricket Club, Leslie Ames Stand Club, Lottery Office Club, Pavilion Club.
